  ![A hands-on photo of Google’s Pixel 9 Pro Fold.](https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25565579/DSCF0084.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100&w=2400)
  
